## ⚠️ Final Step: Adding Credentials

To make the login work, you need to add your Supabase credentials. 

### Option 1: Tell me the keys
You can simply paste the **URL** and **Anon Key** here in the chat, and I will update the files for you.

### Option 2: Edit manually
Open [supabase-auth.js](file:///d:/14012026Veo%20Automation%20Setup%201.2.1/$PLUGINSDIR/resources/app/dist/supabase-auth.js) and replace the placeholders:
```javascript
const SUPABASE_URL = 'YOUR_SUPABASE_URL_HERE';
const SUPABASE_ANON_KEY = 'YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY_HERE';
```
